#: ../../00-overview.md:1 3bd81c95bd884382824af3aea3830f61
msgid "Lazy Todo App — Project Overview"
msgstr "Lazy Todo App — 项目概览"

#: ../../00-overview.md:5 833562008a354b7091e2d96809c0553f
msgid "Purpose"
msgstr "目标"

#: ../../00-overview.md:7 5678a181d12c48148935c1e362108dd0
msgid ""
"Lazy Todo App is a cross-platform desktop productivity app that combines "
"four closely related capabilities in a single Tauri desktop experience:"
msgstr "Lazy Todo App 是一个跨平台桌面效率应用，在一个 Tauri 桌面体验中整合了四项紧密相关的能力："

#: ../../00-overview.md:9 9cbdb506619240c4a93a6d5d7288413b
msgid ""
"**Todo management** with priorities, deadlines, countdowns, search, and "
"list/grid display options"
msgstr "**Todo 管理**：支持优先级、截止时间、倒计时、搜索以及列表/网格显示模式"

#: ../../00-overview.md:10 bafd1df9e50344d8a01a43d8732748a1
msgid ""
"**Sticky notes** with Markdown rendering, color themes, inline editing, "
"and dedicated pop-out note windows"
msgstr "**即时贴**：支持 Markdown 渲染、颜色主题、内联编辑以及独立弹出便签窗口"

#: ../../00-overview.md:11 a016a03cf76f485288e89f3f31cb8c73
msgid ""
"**Pomodoro focus timer** with configurable work/break cycles, milestone "
"tracking, notifications, and weekly stats"
msgstr "**番茄钟专注计时器**：支持可配置的工作/休息周期、里程碑跟踪、通知提醒与每周统计"

#: ../../00-overview.md:12 6a11e35c5cc1412887ee4369b54997f1
msgid ""
"**Application settings** for display preferences, note templates, storage"
" hints, and persistence behavior"
msgstr "**应用设置**：用于配置显示偏好、便签模板、存储提示与持久化行为"

#: ../../00-overview.md:14 eba48ce195aa4ea88e8a902694bc6c5c
msgid ""
"The project is also a practical [Harness "
"Engineering](https://www.fanyamin.com/tech/harness-engineering.html) case"
" study: the codebase is intentionally structured so AI agents can "
"contribute safely by following explicit architecture rules."
msgstr ""
"该项目也是一个实用的 [Harness Engineering](https://www.fanyamin.com/tech/harness-engineering.html) "
"案例：代码库被刻意组织成一种结构，使 AI Agent 可以在明确架构规则的约束下安全参与贡献。"

