#: ../../00-overview.md:29 b73e61a48be24f98947fe9bbc74eca18
msgid "Key Characteristics"
msgstr "关键特性"

#: ../../00-overview.md:31 b897e9c25d024d839d01287facec6741
msgid ""
"**Single-binary desktop app**: the main window and note windows are "
"packaged together with Tauri."
msgstr "**单二进制桌面应用**：主窗口与便签窗口一并由 Tauri 打包发布。"

#: ../../00-overview.md:32 3a59540adb0b4e2d820b943a8fdf6bea
msgid ""
"**Offline-first**: the app has no backend service dependency; all data is"
" local."
msgstr "**离线优先**：应用不依赖后端服务，所有数据都保存在本地。"

#: ../../00-overview.md:33 389cff77a37243f1817bfab09ac64125
msgid ""
"**Multi-window note experience**: a note can be opened into its own "
"focused window while still sharing the same SQLite store."
msgstr "**多窗口便签体验**：单条便签可以在独立窗口中打开，同时继续共享同一个 SQLite 存储。"

#: ../../00-overview.md:34 96156bfa6b114ca8a2e52cc272c29c92
msgid ""
"**Configurable persistence**: database location is resolved from "
"`LAZY_TODO_DB_DIR`, then `~/.config/lazy-todo-app/config.json`, then the "
"platform app-data directory."
msgstr ""
"**可配置持久化**：数据库路径解析顺序为 `LAZY_TODO_DB_DIR`、`~/.config/lazy-todo-app/config.json`，"
"最后才是平台默认应用数据目录。"

#: ../../00-overview.md:35 85f0ff67792c4280ae1901abc481632e
msgid ""
"**Tray-centric UX**: the main window hides on close, can be toggled from "
"the tray, and exposes a quick \"New Note\" action."
msgstr "**以托盘为中心的交互体验**：主窗口关闭时会隐藏，可从托盘切换显示，并提供快速“新建便签”操作。"

#: ../../00-overview.md:37 7e196550c9a5435e83facf12506db95b
msgid "Deployment"
msgstr "部署"

#: ../../00-overview.md:39 88c0de4f05d64de7832f5c2f16614672
msgid ""
"The app targets macOS, Linux, and Windows. Production bundles are created"
" with `npm run tauri build`, and the repo now includes a GitHub Actions "
"release workflow in `.github/workflows/release.yml` so tagged builds can "
"publish downloadable installers on GitHub Releases."
msgstr ""
"该应用面向 macOS、Linux 和 Windows。生产构建通过 `npm run tauri build` 生成，"
"仓库中还包含 `.github/workflows/release.yml` GitHub Actions 发布流程，使带标签的构建可以自动把可下载安装包发布到 GitHub Releases。"

